snippet: Chelsea staged a thrilling comeback to beat Steaua Bucharest, 3-1, and reach the Europa League quarterfinals, but Inter Milan failed to advance despite a plucky second-leg recovery.
abstract: Chelsea defeats Steaua Bucharest, 3-1, to reach soccer's Europa League quarterfinals.
lead_paragraph: Chelsea staged a thrilling comeback to beat Steaua Bucharest, 3-1, and reach the Europa League quarterfinals, but Inter Milan failed to advance despite a plucky second-leg recovery.
